headline: Gameberry Labs Makes History with the Launch of the First-Ever Stand-Alone Mobile App for the Iconic Board Game SORRY!
summary: Gameberry Labs, a global leader in multiplayer mobile games, has collaborated with leading games, IP and toy company Hasbro (NASDAQ: HAS) to launch SORRY! WORLD - the first-ever stand-alone mobile app for the beloved and iconic board game SORRY!.
